googleVisit: How likely are you to visit this news website if it looked as you see above?
clickHeadline: How likely are you to click on the news headlines when presented this way?
clickImages: How likely are you to click on the news images next to the headlines when presented this way?
readHeadline: How likely are you to read the news headlines when presented this way?
seeImages: How likely are you to focus on the news images next to the headlines when presented this way?
